189
00:09:49,500 --> 00:09:50,930
<font color=#FFFF00>[Jang Do Han Menjadi Saksi Pembunuhan]</font>

190
00:09:52,790 --> 00:09:54,390
<font color=#FFFF00>Daejang barusan bilang apa?</font>

191
00:09:54,390 --> 00:09:56,630
<font color=#FFFF00>Saat Yoon Shi Wan membawa Yu Na ke atap gedung,</font>

192
00:09:56,630 --> 00:09:58,230
<font color=#FFFF00>Daejang di sana.</font>

193
00:09:59,090 --> 00:10:02,260
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa kau menyadari yang baru saja kau katakan, Jaksa Jang?</font>

194
00:10:02,560 --> 00:10:04,890
<font color=#FFFF00>Bila Jaksa Jang berada di TKP,</font>

195
00:10:05,260 --> 00:10:09,930
<font color=#FFFF00>artinya kau pun bertanggung-jawab karena membiarkan Yoon Shi Wan
