196
00:10:10,430 --> 00:10:11,760
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau menyadarinya?</font>

197
00:10:12,590 --> 00:10:14,230
<font color=#FFFF00>Membiarkan pembunuhan,</font>

198
00:10:15,230 --> 00:10:16,690
<font color=#FFFF00>kau mengakuinya?</font>

199
00:10:19,230 --> 00:10:20,430
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya.</font>

200
00:10:23,360 --> 00:10:24,530
<font color=#FFFF00>Saya...</font>

201
00:10:26,030 --> 00:10:28,630
<font color=#FFFF00>...bisa saja menghentikan Shi Wan melakukan pembunuhan.</font>

202
00:10:30,230 --> 00:10:32,630
<font color=#FFFF00>Saya bisa mencegah kematian Yu Na.</font>

203
00:10:35,890 --> 00:10:37,160
<font color=#FFFF00>Namun,</font>

204
00:10:40,560 --> 00:10:42,030
