213
00:11:02,530 --> 00:11:04,230
<font color=#FFFF00>Jajak pendapat akan ditunda.</font>

214
00:11:04,690 --> 00:11:05,760
<font color=#FFFF00>Sekarang,</font>

215
00:11:06,030 --> 00:11:07,990
<font color=#FFFF00>kesaksian dari Jang Do Han...</font>

216
00:11:07,990 --> 00:11:09,960
<font color=#FFFF00>...dalam kasus putra Kandidat Yoon,</font>

217
00:11:09,960 --> 00:11:12,160
<font color=#FFFF00>beserta segala pernyataan kandidat...</font>

218
00:11:12,560 --> 00:11:15,230
<font color=#FFFF00>...akan dilanjutkan dalam jajak pendapat besok.</font>

219
00:11:15,230 --> 00:11:18,190
