310
00:19:23,890 --> 00:19:26,860
<font color=#FFFF00>- Kau masuk saja ke kamarmu.
- <i>...tepat waktu.</i></font>

311
00:19:27,090 --> 00:19:29,160
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku membaca artikelnya di internet.</font>

312
00:19:33,460 --> 00:19:36,130
<font color=#FFFF00>Yeobo, kau baik-baik saja?</font>

313
00:19:36,890 --> 00:19:38,060
<font color=#FFFF00>Selamat datang.</font>

314
00:19:39,590 --> 00:19:41,830
<font color=#FFFF00>Tak apa, semuanya akan baik-baik saja.</font>

315
00:19:42,730 --> 00:19:45,890
<font color=#FFFF00>Sungguh Shi Wan tidak akan dapat masalah, 'kan?</font>

316
00:19:46,460 --> 00:19:47,860
<font color=#FFFF00>Kita lihat saja besok.</font>

317
00:20:27,360 --> 00:20:28,860
<font color=#FFFF00>Bagaimana riwayat panggilannya?</font>

318
00:20:30,090 --> 00:20:33,230
<font color=#FFFF00>Baiklah, dan lagi aku ingin kau...</font>

319
00:20:33,230 --> 00:20:35,360
<font color=#FFFF00>...membawakan beberapa dokumen ke jajak pendapat besok.</font>

320
00:20:36,560 --> 00:20:39,930
<font color=#FFFF00>Begitu? Kerja bagus. Ya.</font>

321
00:20:53,990 --> 00:20:56,030
<font color=#FFFF00>Anda menyimpan ponsel Nam Hyeongsa, bukan?</font>

322
00:20:56,360 --> 00:20:57,430
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya.</font>

323
00:20:57,490 --> 00:20:59,360
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa tidak mengatakannya pada saya?</font>

324
00:21:02,360 --> 00:21:04,230
<font color=#FFFF00>Kapan saya bisa mendapatkannya?</font>

325
00:21:53,130 --> 00:21:54,430
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Kau sedang apa?</i></font>

326
00:21:55,190 --> 00:21:56,830
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Kau pergi tanpa pamit.</i></font>

327
00:21:57,930 --> 00:21:59,190
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Terjadi sesuatu?</i></font>

328
00:22:34,930 --> 00:22:37,260
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa? Kau masih bangun?</font>

329
00:22:37,560 --> 00:22:39,790
<font color=#FFFF00>A--anu...</font>

330
00:22:41,530 --> 00:22:42,660
<font color=#FFFF00>Eomma.</font>

331
00:22:43,630 --> 00:22:45,890
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa? Terjadi sesuatu?</font>

332
00:22:46,890 --> 00:22:48,090
<font color=#FFFF00>A--anu..</font>

333
00:22:48,460 --> 00:22:50,990
<font color=#FFFF00>Se--sebenarnya aku...</font>

334
00:22:55,390 --> 00:22:56,930
<font color=#FFFF00>Sebenarnya, hari ini, aku--</font>

335
00:22:56,930 --> 00:22:58,590
<font color=#FFFF00>Sebentar, Se Won. Sebentar.</font>

336
00:22:59,960 --> 00:23:01,130
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya, ada apa?</font>

337
00:23:02,360 --> 00:23:03,360
<font color=#FFFF00>Sungguh?</font>

338
00:23:04,690 --> 00:23:06,590
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku mengerti. Aku akan segera ke sana.</font>

339
00:23:06,590 --> 00:23:08,990
<font color=#FFFF00>Pastikan dia tidak berubah pikiran.</font>

340
00:23:09,390 --> 00:23:10,390
<font color=#FFFF00>Oh.</font>

341
00:23:10,690 --> 00:23:14,130
<font color=#FFFF00>Se Won-ah, Eomma benar-benar minta maaf.</font>

342
00:23:14,130 --> 00:23:16,260
<font color=#FFFF00>Tapi, aku akan segera kembali.</font>

343
00:23:16,260 --> 00:23:18,330
<font color=#FFFF00>Kunci pintunya dan tidurlah, mengerti?</font>

344
00:23:39,260 --> 00:23:40,460
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa masih bangun?</font>

345
00:23:42,460 --> 00:23:44,030
